{"tid":910492,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"新歌難度大增  TWICE周支瑜表演時忘記歌詞 台灣網民：可愛！","createTime":"2018-11-21T08:28:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T09:07:55.000Z","uid":74065,"like":7,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9a12a025dafb01ad90f8a5bb9d605d29300611d1","tid":910492,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T08:28:10.000Z","msg":"TWICE在音樂中心上播放了新歌「YES OR YES」！。<br />\n網民發現最年輕的成員支瑜在表演時犯了一個小錯誤。<br />\n支瑜的台詞應該是「現在一切都取決於你」，但她只是唱「這完全取決於你」。<br />\n因為一言不發，支瑜的手勢與音樂不符。<br />\n<img src=\"https://kbizoom.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/tzuyu1-1.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkbizoom.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2Ftzuyu1-1.webp&h=70be5370&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唱錯歌詞<br />\n<img src=\"https://kbizoom.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/tzuyu2.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkbizoom.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2Ftzuyu2.webp&h=e6a82b7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n動作偏離了音樂<br />\n<img src=\"https://kbizoom.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/tzuyu3.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkbizoom.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2Ftzuyu3.webp&h=f1d33f3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舞台上既出錯已經變成習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0899fdd86ecfc64a7f666afe32b1cb2e1bca33cc","tid":910492,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T08:29:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UPTTQqV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUPTTQqV.gif&h=4313a865&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o0SxmxB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo0SxmxB.gif&h=ea82f3b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d79f3LY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"http